data.description: Brimming with coastal charm, this 3 bedroom home is perfectly situated to take advantage of all Warrenton has to offer. Enjoy summer afternoons in the oversized yard or spend cozy winter days inside by the fireplace. Other features include butcher block counter tops, an oversized laundry and mud room, an extra room with plumbing access for a second bathroom, and two out buildings.
